<h2>Chapter 7: Link Building for Contractors</h2>
<p><a href="/glossary/link-building/">Link building</a> for home service businesses is different from other industries. You do not need backlinks from tech blogs. You need links from local directories, trade associations, suppliers, and community organizations.</p>
<h3>Citations and Local Directories</h3>
<p>A <a href="/glossary/citation/">citation</a> is any online mention of your business name, address, and phone number (NAP). Consistent citations across major directories strengthen local rankings.</p>
