<li>[ ] Nextdoor</li>
<li>[ ] Facebook Business</li>
<li>[ ] Apple Maps</li>
<li>[ ] Bing Places</li>
<li>[ ] Thumbtack</li>
</ul>
<p>Use the <a href="/best/local-seo-tools/">best local SEO tools</a> to manage citations across platforms. Accuracy matters more than quantity. One wrong phone number can split your ranking signals.</p>
<h3>Trade-Specific Link Opportunities</h3>
<p>Each trade has unique link sources that competitors often miss:</p>
<p><strong>Plumbers:</strong>
- Supplier websites (Ferguson, Roto-Rooter franchise directories)
